btrplace.plan

Class DefaultReconfigurationPlan

  • java.lang.Object
    • btrplace.plan.DefaultReconfigurationPlan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ReconfigurationPlan, Iterable<Action>

    public class DefaultReconfigurationPlan
extends Object
implements ReconfigurationPlan
    Default implementation for ReconfigurationPlan. By default, the instance relies on a TimeBasedPlanApplier to check for the plan applicability.
    Author:
    Fabien Hermenier
